data.description: Beautiful, spacious open floor plan. Located in North West Fresno, in a great neighborhood on a cul-de-sac. This home is ready for new owners. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths, a family room and living room plus a formal dining room. The fully equipped kitchen has laminate flooring. The large primary bedroom has a high vaulted ceilings. Mature landscaping in the front and back with lots of room for entertaining. Home has solar and is located close to schools and shopping. A must see, call today!
